Kindergarten is part, too, have understood the architects.
The administrative building avriopoint of Brno is the new headquarters of the arch design.
Nobody would have expected that also houses a mini nursery school with everything it needs — the walls of imaginative colours, furniture, toys and finally a miniature playground on the terrace.
Since October last year, can make children of employees of arch. design.
The society of projets-architectonique design. arch. The workshops had produced a large number of buildings in Brno, has imagined his mini Nursery School of Business since the first drafts of the building avriopoint.
It employs about 90 people, mainly of the age to have children and it was important that women architects and project leaders can quickly return to work.
At the same time as labour contracts in time decreased, nursery school is a proposed bonuses to its employees by society design. arch. In the framework of the social agenda.
Builders and architects have the possibility to combine a job taking with the care for children.
It is the employees of arch.design.eux-mêmes have imagined this nursery school and with the support of the direction they were able to obtain funding from the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mini nursery school is funded by the European Social Fund through the operational programme for human resources and the State budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to the availability of funding (2.8 mil.de Koruny). They were able to purchase equipment and appliances and after two years for qualified personnel as well as the road.
After the use of funding (two years), the company arch. Design. obligation after 3 years to operate the mini nursery school on its own funds.
The preparation of the project lasted a year and it is the economy rating that has helped to make the request.
The care for children is provided by qualified staff, all day, a nurse and a kindergarten teacher in enfants. children can go to school, without age restrictions but they have more than three years.
As it is a "mini nursery school" there can only be 5 children present at the same time, but during the day, there are more who will replace.
The functioning of the school is flexible, depending on the needs of parents and children of all employees have the right to use the school without regard to the hierarchical position.
Although agise an individual care and education, the programme of the mini nursery school is comparable to that for pre-school education.
Children are no that play but a quality education is also guaranteed – from the beginning until the preparation for school benches teaches English.
The class is equipped not only to toys and games imaginative but also a computer that children can use.
The presence of small children in society creates a friendly and positive.
Parents may at any time verify their child and not having the stress of a delay to collect the children in a school near the place of work of parents.
Parents use their time more productively.
It is not surprising that creates a natural relationship of loyalty between the employee and the employer.
Arch.design.s' is included among the companies that offer a bonus of choice for recruitment of new employees and that are friendly towards the family and through this programme enhances the marketing of RH.
The House still fascinates bones after 100 years. Take a look in the English of Gaudi.
The toît looks like the back of a prehistoric saurien, the staircase to a backbone of dinosaur and balconies to fish gueules open.
It is thus the House Casa battlo Barcelona architect Antoni Gaudi's.
Because of its Organic forms, the House has received from the local nickname into bone.
Organic forms, colors, unusual use wild, fragments of stone tiles and mosaîque, facade Recalling flakes curves and present everywhere, this is everything ypique for the new art of Antoni Gaudi.
The front facade of the House conducted its lines of dream, its colours and textures visually reminiscent of nature and animals.
In a more detailed comment is the geometry, the pace and thought with precision.
On the night the facade of the House becomes even more dramatic and activated the impression of glitter colours is strengthened.
The winding and twisting forms also appears in the English with the same measure.
Timber copy in vague bundles of windows, the decorative balustrades, the doors, the oeilleton and strips.
The House battlo which runs in the eixample district in the Passeig de Gracia merchant street at number 43, is born of the construction of a house in 1877 by the architect Emilio Sala Cortes.
The reconstruction is made for two years and the House completed in 1906.
The investor, Joseph battlo, a wealthy entrepreneur, was first placed on the demolition of the vieile construction and the construction of another new but quickly accepted the idea of unusual Gaudi reconstruction and cheaper.
But the idea of Casa battlo as house in multiple housing was not thought by Gaudi alone.
The architect Josep Maria jujol worked with him.
It is precisely on its project that are born the decorations for an apartment of representation of the owner of the building and use the mosaîque window-dressing.
For the facade also worked for other artists and creators.
The joint work plans for the House, Casa battlo began by cooperation between succés jujol and Gaudi.
Jujol participated in building the house of Gaudi Casa Mila and guell park where there are other works of Gaudi.
Locals have nicknamed the hot House just after its completion because of its Organic forms' home in bones ".
Further, with regard to the specific mechanism of opening windows have called "the House baille".
It said that the building there is a sword similar to that of St George, the patron saint of Catalonia.
Other elements of sculpture of construction contain religious motives hidden.
Gaudi was thought to house a single system in his time with central heating, ventilating vents and chimneys characteristic.
Their angle of 45 degrees seems odd.
During the establishment Gaudi has not followed the guidelines of construction and has not left stand by them.
At the beginning of construction he obtained from the city the permits, knowing of course that the data entered on reconstruction plans were so vague that during the two years after finishing the City Council was horrified and demanded changes.
He did not like, for example, members of the City Council that the pillars of the construction empiettent public on the sidewalk.
There were ever to change, but, on the contrary, only 15 days after the appeal of the city Josep battlo demanded (and got satisfaction) permission to rent the top two floors.
The owner déménagea to lower floors.
In the gallery on the second floor, there was a common Lounge and the third a Chamber and a closed part of the apartment.
The ground floor was leased to a jewellery store.
The full house of six floors is shared by a staircase by which access up to a balcony of toît independent.
All angles and straight lines were cancelled by the basic elements of the reconstruction and their replacement by walls curves.
Gaudi also worked the modern concept of the spaces.
The municipality may be connected completely by opening the doors of the exhibition and the high society can communicate comfortably or confined space for private interviews, more intimate.
The House with the reconstruction of Gaudi has also received a new facades toîture non-traditional and two floors apart.
The game of Gaudi with the light is also impressive, of blue and white glazed tile, which is decorated with the domestic court and sinks of enlightenment.
The stake in two colours give a maximum of light across the floors of the House.
It was enough simply to bet on the principle that white reflête more than the bleak instead absorbs the sun's rays.
The House Casa battlo which was included in the UNESCO World Heritage may be visited by each.
The first floor of the apartment house is the largest and most splendid accessible to the public.
The owners have decided to take this step in 2002 on the occasion of the 150th anniversary of the birth of the famous creator.
They continued the visits because they have found it is a lucrative business and they have broadened the scope of visits to the common spaces and the attic including toît terraces.
The entry ticket to the monument is not really expensive and cost €16.50; students, pensioners, groups and tourist card holders have 20 per cent discounts.
The sum is still above the price of entry into the other Gaudi buildings in the city.
If you want to feel the atmosphere of the House with its fantastic shock struts, you quickly find a comrade among residents of the building completely and visit the House.
How to choose a mattress and a sommier: women have other criteria as men.
Not ostentatious framework, but rather the quality of the surface for the bed, so the mattress and sommier provide a real basis for a good read.
Of course they should harmoniously complement each other to please a user concrete.
During the selection of several things are essential: the weight, size, age, state of health, and the sex of the owner.
The type of procedure in which it will place the mattress and sommier is also important.
A typical example?
For example, in the cottage where it never sleeps continually latex mattresses are not appropriate because they are "warm" slowly.
They also have a higher weight to mattresses in standard polyurethane.
It is necessary to return frequently.
If they do not have enough ventilation channels in the heart and if they are, in addition, on a solid, they hold moisture. The mould may also be formed.
The habit is also decisive in the choice.
That is the clear time abroad where it often uses mattresses very thick with a layer rammollissante, feels ill on a surface low and hard.
"This is so that all hokeyistes returning from NHL complain that they cannot sleep there".
"for their shoulders tired, legs and ribs, they needed mattress with a layer of foam rammollisante lazy".
"Such mattresses are also recommended for people who suffer from diabetes, who have a disorder of the nervous system that is failing" information "of the joints and the skin," explained adamczikova Sylva, who specializes in the upholstered furniture.
It is for this reason that a few years ago the mattress with foam lazy won the hokeyistes so that other customers.
"Today everything went well, tempur, Italian magnifex but Czech growers, for example appropriate mattresses.
You do not need to be a guy of NHL to assess a foam lazy.
This "miracle" is simply.
She optimalise its rigidity and his form in the heat absorbed or adapts to the warmth of your body.
There is no pressure on you and you do not go back into the night as after a difficult match.
You simply dormez better.
The foam lazy also functions as a protection against esquarres.
For the choice of mattresses, depending on your size, add the length of the feet, or about 21 / 34 cm.
A man and a woman from a size of 180cm therefore need a bed of 210 / 220 cm.
The minimum width for each for a bed to two places should be 90 cm is 180 cm.
For beds in one place, the singles, for example, it is recommended to be at least 120 / 140 cm.
It is easy to visit.
"However, there is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on its back, you should ask the hands so comfortable with the elbows slightly folded. Helena prokopova, President of the Association of bourreliers-matelassiers decorators and focused for several years on the issue of a healthy sleep and ergonomic furniture and taught in the schools.
For a bed for two everyone needs its own sommier and mattresses, therefore, attention during the achât to choose the height of the mattress.
Otherwise you will to mount the sommier at different heights and that is not achievable in all settings.
The foam mattress should have a minimum height of 14 cm, mattresses to springs at least 15 cm, this count for the layer of form and venting at least three centimetres.
"The touch or while seated on the mattress you must not feel springs," warns Héléna prokopova.
Each mattress request a specific type of sommier.
The lit-sommier, when the mattress and sommier are together as sisters siamoises, has nothing to do in the bedrooms.
The mattress is aèrent badly; we must not wash, which is commonly auhourd' today.
And as for the night is normally very 0.2 to 0.75 l sweat it is clear that after 5 / 7 years, the mattress starts to recall a great (and sieve filled).
For this the specialists refuse to make the claims on a lifetime of 25 years for a mattress or a guarantee for life.
But its but.
And that a Council of experience on the part of sellers: for a mattress of 120 / 140cm, dispensing, to the surface of the mattress, hygiene and cleaning but rather Jolly mattress of protection that vouspouvez easily withdraw and washing.
And even if these days it is common for manufacturing of coatings with closure to slide for the whole, that is to say that after the opening it was two parts (for washing and the size of a washing machine that is very important!) if not manipulation for large models (and for a single person) becomes when cut a battle between a light weight and a lorry on a ring.
You have in your bed a rigid wall instead of a sommier?
Never!
The maximum for a bed for the visitors for a single night.
However équipez do (if there are not) ventilation holes and use the mattress to springs with a minimum height of 70 cm with springs in sachets taschenfederken (Germany) and a layer of ventilation.
A polyurethane mattress should not be part of such a bed.
For the beams to strips to unique position with 14 / 18 strips, the so-called latex mattresses or sandwich (perhaps the combination of rubber and coconut), are the ideal but it will always be better for you to have a mattress with more strips, 28 and above, where the strips are doubled in the bottom of the kidneys, and that it is possible to regulate the rigidity.
For the mattress at several positions it must not take mattresses to springs because it does not respond to changes in position.
Besides setting the rigidity of the strips can install also known as a cradle of shoulder.
It is a special link strips that can push even tilt the gills are allowed for the shoulder of dormeur "fits well.
For men who have "the shoulders as wide as the back ', it really is an important issue.
This thing is already envisaged by the manufacturers of mattresses that for "masculine" began to use a rammollissante zone at the shoulders.
But they also believe the women - they offer a more sluggish surface at the hips.
For the customer, the more difficult the beams to wings or pamphlets with so-called multiforce suspension.
The pressure is given in more points and diinue tension.
But of course, when you use a pillow (large and inflated) on good mattresses and sommier, the "more" disparait.
The basic rule is a pillow quite simple: the pillow should support the head and its spines should meet only the shoulders, so that the muscles of the shoulders can rest.
The recommended size is 50x60 cm as the Scandinavians by exmple prefer.
When one is lying on its side, the pillow must upgrade (with the cradle of the shoulder sommier rammollie or zone in the mattress) the height of the shoulders.
The modern mattresses still have something in common with the first straw and grass.
Manufacturers still use natural substances or mixtures.
The trend is also on mattresses bio.
