Almost all known manufacturers use precisely the soya.
"the word bio for the mattress means that the heart is manufactured from natural products," said Petr vasicek growers society.
The natural materials are used also for coatings mattresses; one of the first was the Aloe Vera.
But you can add micro-capsules of perfumes in the forest or lavande.
There are differences between men and women.
While the birch extracted from plants on the surface of the mattress absorbs heat and cool down the body, "cool," the "heat" women.
The excerpt of red pepper, boosts blood circulation and is therefore hotter for the weaker sex.
The current favourite?
The mattress made from foam cold (it has more pores with a cellular disrupted more than the standard polyurethane respirante and has more elasticity.
The combination of different rigidity of cold call foam mattresses polyzones who know exactly where is the head, the lower back and feet.
You pay a mattress of quality from 7000 kronor and more.
Those who are characterized by their parameters for health have less VAT and are used as instruments for health.
