Then, Michael becomes nervous.
"It is high time you déguerpissiez" announced the robust oil worker.
"The soldiers can arise at any time."
If the illegal refiners are surprised by special units of the armed forces, they are not the subject of an arrest, but at best they will offer bribes.
Even the most soldiers from the north of the country will benefit as all Nigerians from the first.
